Anborn can be found in Henneth Annûn.\n\nAnborn is telling you what he recalls of the night he brought the gangrel-creature to be questioned.
Anborn recalls bringing Gollum forth to be questioned by Faramir shortly after his capture, and his fears for the journey of the Halflings and the gangrel-creature.
'At my lord's request, I goaded the gangrel-creature forth to answer for his intrusion...'
'That is all I recall of that night, my friend.'
'I led the creature away, and he rested, but never did my eyes leave him...'
